\id EZR - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020
\h Ezra
\toc1 Ezra
\toc2 Ezra
\toc3 Ezr
\mt1 Ezra
\c 1
\s1 Sairas okonyo joma ni e twech odwogo
\p 
\v 1 E higa mokwongo mar loch Sairas ruodh Pasia, mondo ochop singo mar wach Jehova Nyasaye mane Jeremia okoro, Jehova Nyasaye nowuoyo gi chuny Sairas ruodh Pasia mondo ogol lendo e pinye duto koketo e ndiko kama:
\pmo 
\v 2 Ma e gima Sairas ruodh Pasia wacho:
\pm “ ‘Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach polo, osemiya pinjeruodhi duto manie piny kendo oseyiera mondo agerne hekalu e Jerusalem manie piny Juda.
\v 3 Ngʼato angʼata kuom joge manie dieru, mad Nyasache bed kode, mondo odhi Jerusalem man Juda mi oger hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach Israel, Nyasaye man Jerusalem.
\v 4 To ji moa kamoro amora ma joma otony nyalo bet ni koro odakie mondo ochiwne fedha gi dhahabu, kod gik miuso gi kweth mag dhok, to gi chiwo mar hera ne hekalu mar Nyasaye e Jerusalem.’ ”
\p 
\v 5 Eka jotend anywola mar Juda kod Benjamin, gi jodolo kod jo-Lawi, ngʼato angʼata ma Nyasaye nomulo chunye, noikore dhi kendo gero od Jehova Nyasaye man Jerusalem.
\v 6 Jobathgi duto noyworogi gi gige fedha kod dhahabu, kod gik miuso gi kweth mag dhok, kod mich ma nengone tek, kaachiel gi chiwo mar hera.
\p 
\v 7 Kata kamano, Ruoth Sairas nochiwo gigo mane mag hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, mane Nebukadneza oyudo osegolo Jerusalem mi otero e hekalu mar nyasache.
\v 8 Sairas ruodh Pasia nowacho ni okelgi gi jakeno, Mithredath, mane okwanogi ne Sheshbaza jatend Juda.
\b
\li4 
\v 9 Ma e kwan gik mane ochiw:
\b
\li1 Dise mag dhahabu piero adek,
\li1 dise mag fedha alufu achiel,
\li1 kareche mag fedha piero ariyo gochiko,
\li1 
\v 10 bakunde mag dhahabu piero adek,
\li1 bakunde machalre mag fedha mia angʼwen gapar,
\li1 gik mamoko mitiyogo alufu achiel.
\b
\li4 
\v 11 Gigo duto mane itiyogo mane olosi gi dhahabu kod fedha noromo alufu abich kod mia angʼwen.
\b
\p Sheshbaza nobiro gi gigi duto e kinde mane joma ne otwe noa Babulon kadhi Jerusalem.
\c 2
\s1 Kwan kod nying joma ne otwe mane odwogo
\li4 
\v 1 Koro magi e joma noa e gwenge manoduogo koa e twech Babulon, kuma Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon noterogie. Negidwogo Jerusalem kod Juda, ka moro ka moro dok e dalane owuon,
\v 2 ka gin kanyakla gi Zerubabel, Jeshua, Nehemia, Seraya, Relaya, Modekai, Bilshan, Mispar, Bigvai, Rehum kod Baana.
\b
\li4 Kar kwan mar nying jo-Israel machwo e magi.
\li1 
\v 3 Nyikwa Parosh, ji alufu ariyo mia achiel gi piero abiriyo gariyo (2,172),
\li1 
\v 4 nyikwa Shefatia, ji mia adek gi piero abiriyo gariyo (372),
\li1 
\v 5 nyikwa Ara, ji mia abiriyo gi piero abiriyo gabich (775),
\li1 
\v 6 nyikwa Pahath-Moab (mowuok e dhood Jeshua gi Joab), ji alufu ariyo mia aboro gi apar gariyo (2,812),
\li1 
\v 7 nyikwa Elam, ji alufu achiel mia ariyo gi piero abich gangʼwen (1,254),
\li1 
\v 8 nyikwa Zatu, ji mia ochiko gi piero angʼwen gabich (945),
\li1 
\v 9 nyikwa Zakai, ji mia abiriyo gi piero auchiel (760),
\li1 
\v 10 nyikwa Bani, ji mia auchiel gi piero angʼwen gariyo (642),
\li1 
\v 11 nyikwa Bebai, ji mia auchiel gi piero ariyo gadek (623),
\li1 
\v 12 nyikwa Azgad, ji alufu achiel mia ariyo gi piero ariyo gariyo (1,222),
\li1 
\v 13 nyikwa Adonikam, ji mia auchiel gi piero auchiel gauchiel (666),
\li1 
\v 14 nyikwa Bigvai, ji alufu ariyo gi piero abich gauchiel (2,056),
\li1 
\v 15 nyikwa Adin, ji mia angʼwen gi piero abich gangʼwen (454),
\li1 
\v 16 nyikwa Ater (kowuok e dhood Hezekia), ji piero ochiko gaboro (98),
\li1 
\v 17 nyikwa Bezai, ji mia adek gi piero adek gadek (323)
\li1 
\v 18 nyikwa Jora, ji mia achiel gi apar gariyo (112),
\li1 
\v 19 nyikwa Hashum, ji mia ariyo gi piero ariyo gadek (223),
\li1 
\v 20 nyikwa Gibar, ji piero ochiko gabich (95),
\b
\li1 
\v 21 jo-Bethlehem, ji mia achiel gi piero ariyo gadek (123),
\li1 
\v 22 nyikwa Netofa, ji piero abich gauchiel (56),
\li1 
\v 23 nyikwa Anathoth, ji mia achiel gi piero ariyo gaboro (128),
\li1 
\v 24 nyikwa Azmaveth, ji piero angʼwen gariyo (42),
\li1 
\v 25 nyikwa Kiriath Jearim, Kefira kod Beeroth, ji mia abiriyo gi piero angʼwen gadek (743),
\li1 
\v 26 nyikwa Rama kod Geba, ji mia auchiel gi piero ariyo gachiel (621),
\li1 
\v 27 nyikwa Mikmash, ji mia achiel gi piero ariyo gariyo (122),
\li1 
\v 28 nyikwa Bethel kod Ai, ji mia ariyo gi piero ariyo gadek (223),
\li1 
\v 29 nyikwa Nebo, ji piero abich gariyo (52),
\li1 
\v 30 nyikwa Magbish, ji mia achiel gi piero abich gauchiel (156),
\li1 
\v 31 nyikwa Elam moko, ji alufu achiel mia ariyo gi piero abich gangʼwen (1,254),
\li1 
\v 32 nyikwa Harim, ji mia adek gi piero ariyo (320)
\li1 
\v 33 nyikwa Lod, Hadid kod Ono, ji mia abiriyo gi piero ariyo gabich (725),
\li1 
\v 34 nyikwa Jeriko, ji mia adek gi piero angʼwen gabich (345),
\li1 
\v 35 nyikwa Sena, ji alufu adek mia auchiel gi piero adek (3,630).
\b
\li4 
\v 36 Jodolo ne gin:
\li1 nyikwa Jedaya (mowuok e dhood Jeshua), ji mia ochiko gi piero abiriyo gadek (973),
\li1 
\v 37 nyikwa Imer, ji alufu achiel gi piero abich gariyo (1,052),
\li1 
\v 38 nyikwa Pashur, ji alufu achiel mia ariyo gi piero angʼwen gabiriyo (1,247),
\li1 
\v 39 nyikwa Harim, ji alufu achiel gi apar gabiriyo (1,017).
\b
\li4 
\v 40 Jo-Lawi ne gin:
\li1 nyikwa Jeshua kod Kadmiel (mowuok e dhood Hodavia), ji piero abiriyo gangʼwen (74).
\b
\li4 
\v 41 Jower ne gin:
\li1 Nyikwa Asaf, ji mia achiel gi piero ariyo gaboro (128).
\b
\li4 
\v 42 Jorit dhoranga hekalu ne gin:
\li1 Nyikwa Shalum, Ater, Talmon, Akub, Hatita kod Shobai, ji mia achiel gi piero adek gochiko (139).
\b
\li4 
\v 43 Jotij hekalu ne gin:
\li2 nyikwa
\li2 Ziha, Hasufa, Tabaoth,
\li2 
\v 44 Keros, Siaha, Padon,
\li2 
\v 45 Lebana, Hagaba, Akub,
\li2 
\v 46 Hagab, Shalmai, Hanan,
\li2 
\v 47 Gidel, Gahar, Reaya,
\li2 
\v 48 Rezin, Nekoda, Gazam,
\li2 
\v 49 Uza, Pasea, Besai,
\li2 
\v 50 Asna, Meunim, Nefusim,
\li2 
\v 51 Bakbuk, Hakufa, Harhur,
\li2 
\v 52 Bazluth, Mehida, Harsha,
\li2 
\v 53 Barkos, Sisera, Tema,
\li2 
\v 54 Nezia kod Hatifa.
\li1 
\v 55 Nyikwa jotij Solomon ne gin:
\li2 nyikwa
\li2 Sotai, Hasofereth, Peruda,
\li2 
\v 56 Jaala, Darkon, Gidel,
\li2 
\v 57 Shefatia, Hatil,
\li2 Pokereth-Hazebaim kod Ami.
\li4 
\v 58 Jotij hekalu kod nyikwa jotij Solomon, ji mia adek gi piero ochiko gariyo (392).
\b
\li4 
\v 59 Magi e joma nobiro koa e mier mag Tel Mela, Tel Harsha, Kerub, Adon, kod Imer, to ne ok ginyal nyiso malongʼo ni anywolagi ne gin nyikwa Israel.
\li1 
\v 60 Nyikwa Delaya, Tobia kod Nekoda noromo ji mia auchiel gi piero abich gariyo (652).
\b
\li4 
\v 61 Mago mane oa kuom jodolo ne gin:
\li1 nyikwa Hobaya, Hakoz kod Barzilai (ngʼatno mane okendo nyar Barzilai ma ja-Gilead to kendo ne iluonge gi nyingno).
\li4 
\v 62 Jogi nomanyo nonro mar anywolagi, to ne ok ginyal yudogi, omiyo nowegi oko mar joka jodolo kaka joma ochido.
\v 63 Jatelo maduongʼ nomiyogi chik mondo kik gicham chiemo moro amora mopwodhi manyaka jadolo bedie ma puonjogi gi Urim kod Thumim.
\b
\li4 
\v 64 Jogi duto noromo ji alufu piero angʼwen gariyo mia adek gi piero auchiel (42,360),
\v 65 kiweyo jotijegi machwo kod mamon mane gin ji alufu abiriyo mia adek gi piero adek gabiriyo (7,337); kendo ne gin gi jower machwo kod mamon maromo ji mia ariyo (200).
\v 66 Ne gin gi farese mia abiriyo gi piero adek gauchiel (736), kanyna mia ariyo gi piero angʼwen gabich (245),
\v 67 ngamia mia angʼwen gi piero adek gabich (435) kod punde alufu auchiel mia abiriyo gi piero ariyo (6,720).
\b
\p 
\v 68 Kane gichopo e od Jehova Nyasaye man Jerusalem, jotend mier mamoko nochiwo chiwo mar hera ne gedo mar od Nyasaye e kare mane entiere chon.
\v 69 Kaluwore gi nyalo mag-gi negichiwone kar keno kuom tijni drachmas alufu piero auchiel gachiel (61,000) mar dhahabu (marom gi kilo mia abich mar dhahabu), minas alufu abich (5,000) mar fedha (marom gi kilo alufu adek mar fedha) kod lep dolo mia achiel.
\p 
\v 70 Jodolo, jo-Lawi, jower, jorit dhorangeye kod jotij hekalu nodak Jerusalem, kaachiel gi joma moko, to jo-Israel mamoko nodak e miechgi.
\c 3
\s1 Gero kendo manyien mar misango
\p 
\v 1 Kane dwe mar abiriyo ochopo kendo jo-Israel nosechako dak e miechgi, negichokore kaka joka ngʼato achiel e Jerusalem.
\v 2 Eka Jeshua wuod Jozadak kod jodolo wetene kod Zerubabel wuod Shealtiel gi jogo mane tiyo kode nochako gero kendo mar misango mar Nyasach Israel mondo time chiwo mar misango miwangʼo pep, kaluwore gi gima ondiki e Chike Musa, ngʼat Nyasaye.
\v 3 Kata obedo nine giluoro joma ne olworogi kamano, negigero kendo mar misango e mise mare mi gichiwo misango miwangʼo pep ne Jehova Nyasaye, misango mokinyi kaachiel gi modhiambo.
\v 4 Bangʼe kaluwore gi gima ondiki, negitimo nyasi mar Sawo mar kiche ka gin gi kwan mar misengini miwangʼo pep mowinjore mar odiechiengʼ ka odiechiengʼ.
\v 5 Bangʼ mano, negichiwo misango miwangʼo pep mapile pile, misango mar Dwe Manyien kod sewni moyier mag Jehova Nyasaye, kaachiel gi mago mokel kaka chiwo mar hera ne Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 6 E odiechiengʼ mokwongo mar dwe mar abiriyo, negichako kelo chiwo mar misengini miwangʼo pep ne Jehova Nyasaye, kata obedo ni mise mar hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye ne pok ochaki.
\s1 Gedo manyien mar hekalu
\p 
\v 7 Eka negichiwo pesa ne jogedo kod funde bao, kendo gichiwo chiemo gi math gi mo ne jo-Sidon gi jo-Turo, mondo omi gikel sirni mag sida koluwo nam koa Lebanon nyaka Jopa, kaluwore gi thuolo mane ochiw gi Sairas ruodh Pasia.
\p 
\v 8 E dwe mar ariyo mar higa mar ariyo bangʼ kane gichopo e od Nyasaye e Jerusalem, Zerubabel wuod Shealtiel, Jeshua wuod Jozadak kod owetege mamoko (jodolo gi jo-Lawi kod jogo duto mane odwogo Jerusalem koa e twech) nochako tich, ka giyiero jo-Lawi moromo higni piero ariyo kod jomadongo mondo ginon gedo mar od Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 9 Jeshua gi yawuote kod owetene gi Kadmiel kod yawuote (ma nyikwa Hodavia) kod yawuot Henadad gi yawuote kod owetene, ma gin jo-Lawi duto, noriwore kanyakla ka gingʼiyo jogo matiyo e od Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 10 Ka jogedo noketo mise mar hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, jodolo korwako lepgi mag dolo ka gin gi turumbete, kod jo-Lawi (ma yawuot Asaf) ka gin-gi ongengʼo, nokawo keregi mondo gipak Jehova Nyasaye, kaka nochan gi Daudi ruodh Israel.
\v 11 Ka gipako Jehova Nyasaye kendo gigoyone erokamano ne giwerne kama:
\q1 “Jehova Nyasaye ber;
\q2 kendo hera mare ne jo-Israel osiko nyaka chiengʼ.”
\m To ji duto nogoyo koko matek mar Pak ne Jehova Nyasaye, nikech mise mar od Jehova Nyasaye noketi.
\v 12 To jodolo machon kod jo-Lawi gi jotend anywola, mane oseneno hekalu mokwongo, noywak matek ka gineno kiketo mise mar hekalu, to ji mamoko nokok gi ilo.
\v 13 Onge ngʼama ne nyalo pogo dwol mar goyo koko mar ilo gi dwol mar ywak, nikech ji nogoyo koko matek, kendo dwolno nowinj gi kuma bor.
\c 4
\s1 Okwed gedo manyien mar hekalu
\p 
\v 1 Ka wasik Juda gi Benjamin nowinjo ni joma notwe ne gero hekalu ne Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach Israel,
\v 2 negibiro ir Zerubabel to gi jotend anywola mi giwacho niya, “We wakonyu gedo nikech Nyasachuno ema wan bende wasebedo ka wachiwone misango nyaka aa kinde Esarhadon ruodh Asuria, mane okelowa kae.”
\p 
\v 3 To Zerubabel, Jeshua kod jotend anywola duto mag Israel nodwokogi niya, “Ok un e achiel kodwa e gero hekalu ne Nyasachwa. Wan kendwa wabiro gedo ne Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach Israel, mana kaka Ruoth Sairas, ma ruodh Pasia, nochikowa.”
\p 
\v 4 Eka joma ni machiegni kodgi nowuok mondo onyos chuny jo-Juda kendo gibed maluor mar dhi nyime gi gedo.
\v 5 Negikawo jongʼad rieko michulo mondo okwedgi kendo orund chenro mag-gi e ndalono duto mar loch Sairas ruodh Pasia kendo nyaka ndalo loch mar Darius ruodh Pasia.
\s1 Kwedo gedo mar hekalu e bwo loch Sakses kod Artaksases
\p 
\v 6 E chakruok mar loch Sakses, ne gidonjone jo-Juda kod jo-Jerusalem.
\p 
\v 7 To e ndalo mag Artaksases ruodh Pasia, Bishlam, Mithredath, Tabel kod joge mamoko moriwore godo ne ondiko baruwa ne Artaksases. Baruwani nondiki e kit ndiko mar jo-Aram kendo gi dho jo-Aram.
\p 
\v 8 Rehum ma jatend lweny kod Shimshai ma jagoro nondiko baruwa marach kuom Jerusalem ne Artaksases ma ruoth kama:
\pmo 
\v 9 Rehum ma jatend lweny kod Shimshai ma jagoro, kanyakla gi jogo mamoko mane gitiyogo, ma gin jongʼad bura kod jotelo motelone joma oa Tripolis, Pasia, Erek, Babulon kod jo-Elam moa Susa,
\v 10 gi joma moko mane Ashurbanipal, ngʼatno maduongʼ kendo moluor noriembo, mi omiyogi kar dak e dala maduongʼ mar Samaria kod kamachielo machiegni gi loka Aora Yufrate.
\p 
\v 11 Ma e baruwa machalo gi baruwa mane giorone.
\pmo Ne Ruoth Artaksases.
\pmo Koa kuom jotichgi modak loka Yufrate.
\pm 
\v 12 Ruoth nyaka ngʼeni, jo-Yahudi mane obiro irwa koa iri osedhi Jerusalem kendo gisechako gero dala maduongʼ mane ongʼanyo kendo ma timbene mono. Gisechako gero ohinga mane osemukore kendo to bende giloso mise mage.
\pm 
\v 13 Kuom mano, ruoth onego ngʼe ni ka dala maduongʼni oger kendo ohinga mage ochung kendo, to onge osuru mibiro chul, kata chiwo kod chudo moro amora kendo pesa ma joka ruoth yudo ok nogol.
\v 14 Nimar wan e bwo chik mar kar dak ruoth kendo ok en gima ber mondo wane ka ruoth ichayo, waoro wachni mondo onyis ruoth,
\v 15 mondo omany kuonde mokanie gik machon mag ruodhi miluwo bangʼ-gi. E ndiko machon mokan ibiro yudo ni dala maduongʼni en dala maduongʼ mangʼanyo, ma thago ruodhi kod gwenge, ma en kar ngʼanyo chakre chon. Mano emomiyo dala maduongʼni nokethi.
\v 16 Wanyiso ruoth ni ka dala maduongʼni oger kendo ohingage ochungi, to onge gima ibiro dongʼ godo e loka mar Aora Yufrate.
\p 
\v 17 Ruoth nooro dwoko kama:
\pmo Ne Rehum jatend lweny, Shimshai jagoro kod jogi mamoko ma utiyogo kanyakla modak Samaria gi kuonde mopogore e loka mar Aora Yufrate.
\pmo Amosou.
\pm 
\v 18 Baruwa mane ioronwa osesomnwa kendo oloki e nyima.
\v 19 Ne achiwo chik kendo nonro notim, kendo noyud ni dala maduongʼni nigi sigana mabor mar ngʼanyone ruodhi kendo en kar wich teko kod wacho weche mag wich teko.
\v 20 Jerusalem osebedo gi ruodhi maroteke ka girito piny Yufrate duto, kendo osuru, chiwo ma ruoth ketone joma otelone, kod chudo moro amora mag gik miloko nochulgi.
\v 21 Koro chiw chik ne jogi mondo giwe tich, mondo omi dala maduongʼni kik ger kendo nyaka an ema achiw chik.
\v 22 Bed motangʼ mondo kik ijwangʼ wachni. Angʼo momiyo wach manyalo kelo hinyruok nyaa, mi lochwa kethre?
\p 
\v 23 Mapiyo nono bangʼ ka baruwa machal gi mane oor ne Ruoth Artaksases nosesom ne Rehum kod Shimshai ma jagoro gi joma gitiyogo kanyakla, negidhi mana gisano Jerusalem ir jo-Yahudi kendo ne gichunogi mondo giwe tich.
\b
\p 
\v 24 Omiyo tich mane ni e od Nyasaye man Jerusalem nochungʼ nyaka e higa mar ariyo mar loch Darius ruodh Pasia.
\c 5
\s1 Barup Tatenai ne Darius
\p 
\v 1 Koro Hagai janabi kod Zekaria janabi, nyakwar Ido, nokorone jo-Yahudi e Juda gi Jerusalem e nying Nyasach Israel, mane nitiere kuomgi.
\v 2 Eka Zerubabel wuod Shealtiel kod Jeshua wuod Jozadak nowuok mondo oti tij gedo mar od Nyasaye e Jerusalem. Kendo jonabi mag Nyasaye ne ni kodgi, kakonyogi.
\p 
\v 3 E kindeno Tatenai, ruodh Yufrate, kod Shetha-Bozenai gi joma gitiyogo kanyakla nodhi irgi kendo openjo niya, “En ngʼa mane omiyou thuolo mar gero hekaluni kendo loso iye?”
\v 4 Gin bende negipenjo niya, “Joma gero odni nying-gi ngʼa?”
\v 5 To Nyasaye ne ni kod jodong jo-Yahudi, omiyo ne ok ochung-gi mondo giwe tich ka pod irito dwoko ma ruoth Darius ondiko gi lwete.
\p 
\v 6 Ma e baruwa machal gi mane Tatenai, ruodh Yufrate, kod Shetha-Bozenai gi joma negitiyogo kanyakla, kod jotend Yufrate, noorone Ruoth Darius.
\v 7 Wach mane giorone ne chalo kama:
\pmo Ne Ruoth Darius:
\b
\pmo Wamosi ahinya.
\b
\pm 
\v 8 Ruoth onego ngʼe nine wadhi e gwengʼ mar Juda, e hekalu mar Nyasaye maduongʼ. Ji gedo gi kite madongo kendo giketo bepe e kore. Tich tiyore e yo modimbore kendo odhi nyime mapiyo e bwo telo margi.
\pm 
\v 9 Ne wamiyo jodongo penjo ka wapenjogi niya, “En ngʼa momiyou thuolo mar gero hekaluni kendo loso iye?”
\v 10 Bende ne wapenjogi nying-gi, mondo omi wandik nying jotendgi ne in.
\pm 
\v 11 Ma e dwoko mane gimiyowa:
\b
\pm Wan jotich mar Nyasach polo kod piny, kendo wagero hekalu manyien mane oger higni mangʼeny mokalo, mano mane ruoth maduongʼ mar Israel ogero kendo otieko.
\v 12 To nikech wuonewa nowangʼo ii Nyasach Polo, nochiwogi ne Nebukadneza ja-Kaldea, ruodh Babulon, ma nomuko hekaluni kendo oriembo ji nyaka Babulon.
\pm 
\v 13 Kata kamano, e higa mokwongo mar Sairas ruodh Babulon, Ruoth Sairas nochiwo chik mondo odni mar Nyasaye oger manyien.
\v 14 Bende nogolo koa e hekalu mar Babulon gige dhahabu gi fedha mar od Nyasaye, gigo mane Nebukadneza okawo koa e hekalu man Jerusalem kendo okelo e hekalu man Babulon. Bangʼe Ruoth Sairas nomiyogi ngʼat ma nyinge Sheshbaza, mane osewalo jatelo,
\v 15 kendo onyise niya, “Kaw gigi kendo idhi mi ikan-gi e hekalu man Jerusalem. Kendo iger manyien od Nyasaye e kare machon.”
\pm 
\v 16 Omiyo ngʼatni miluongo ni Sheshbaza nobiro mi oketo mise mar od Nyasaye e Jerusalem. Kochakore e odiechiengno nyaka sani pod igere to pod ok otieke.
\b
\pm 
\v 17 Omiyo koro ka berne ruoth, to mondo nonro otim e kar keno mag gik machon mar Babulon mondo ne ka Ruoth Sairas nochiwo chik mondo oger manyien od Nyasaye e Jerusalem. Eka ruoth mondo oornwa kaka ongʼado wachni.
\c 6
\s1 Chik ma Darius ogolo
\p 
\v 1 Eka Ruoth Darius nochiwo chik, kendo neginono e kuonde kano gik machon e kar keno man Babulon.
\v 2 Karatas moban noyudi e kama oger motegno mar gengʼo wasigu mar Ekbatana e gwengʼ Media, kendo ma e gima nondik kuome:
\pmo Chenro mar gima biro:
\b
\pm 
\v 3 E higa mokwongo mar loch mar Ruoth Sairas, ruoth nochiwo chik kuom hekalu mar Nyasaye man Jerusalem kama.
\b
\pm We hekalu ger kendo kaka kar chiwo misango, kendo we mise mare keti. Nyaka obedi fut piero aboro gaboro gi nus e bor mare kendo fut piero aboro gaboro e lach mare,
\v 4 kod migawo adek mag kite mochwe kadhi malo gi migawo achiel mag bepe mochungi. Chudo margi mondo chul gi keno moa ka ruoth.
\v 5 Bende, gigo mag dhahabu gi fedha mag od Nyasaye, mane Nebukadneza okawo koa e hekalu mar Jerusalem mi okelo Babulon, nyaka duog kargi e hekalu man Jerusalem; nyaka duog-gi e kar keno e od Nyasaye.
\b
\pm 
\v 6 Koro in, Tatenai, jatelo mar Yufrate, kod Shetha-Bozenai kaachiel gi un, jotelo wetegi mar gwengʼno, suduru mabor gi kanyo.
\v 7 Kik uketh tich hekaluni mar Nyasaye. We jatend jo-Yahudi kod jodong jo-Yahudi oger od Nyasaye e kare.
\pm 
\v 8 Kuom mano, achiwo chik mar gima onego itimne jodong jo-Yahudi e gedo mar odni mar Nyasaye:
\pm Gigo ma jogi otiyogo nyaka chul duto koa e keno mar ka ruoth, moa e pesa mochoki kuom Yufrate, mondo omi tich kik chungʼ.
\v 9 Gimoro amora midwaro kaka nyirwedhi, imbe, nyiimbe mar misango miwangʼo pep ne Nyasach polo, kod ngano, chumbi, divai gi mo, kaka okwa gi jodolo man Jerusalem nyaka migi pile ma ok olewo,
\v 10 mondo omi gichiw misengini ma moro Nyasach polo kendo olam ne ruoth gi yawuote obed gi ngima maber.
\pm 
\v 11 Ewi mano, achiwo chik ni ka ngʼato oketho chikni, to nogol yiend tado mar ode mi gur piny kendo tweye e yien-no.
\v 12 Mad Nyasaye, mosemiyo Nyinge olandore ka, lok ruoth moro amora kata joma tingʼo bedegi malo mondo olok chikni kata oketh hekaluni man Jerusalem.
\pm An, Darius asegolo chik, kendo chikni nyaka chopi ma ok orem.
\s1 Tieko gedo kendo gwedho hekalu
\p 
\v 13 To kuom chik mane Ruoth Darius ooro, Tatenai, jatend Yufrate, kod Shetha-Bozenai gi joma negitiyogo kanyakla notimo kamano kuom tangʼ mathoth.
\v 14 Omiyo jodong jo-Yahudi nodhi nyime gi gedo kendo odhi maber e bwo yalo mar Hagai janabi gi Zekaria, nyakwar Ido. Negitieko gero hekalu kaluwore gi chik mar Nyasach Israel kod chike Sairas, Darius gi Artaksases, ruodhi Pasia.
\v 15 Hekalu notieki gero e odiechiengʼ mar adek mar dwe mar Adar, e higa mar auchiel mar loch Ruoth Darius.
\p 
\v 16 Eka jo-Israel, ma gin jodolo, jo-Lawi kod joma moko mane oa e twech notimo nyasi mar gwedho od Nyasaye gi ilo.
\v 17 Kane gigwedho od Nyasaye negichiwo rwedhi mia achiel, imbe mia ariyo, nyithi rombe machwo mia angʼwen to kaka misango mar golo richo ne Israel, negichiwo diek apar gariyo machwo, moro ka moro ni dhout Israel.
\v 18 Kendo negiketo jodolo kuondegi kod jo-Lawi e migepe mag-gi ne tich Nyasaye e Jerusalem, kaluwore gi gima ondikie Kitap Musa.
\s1 Pasaka
\p 
\v 19 E odiechiengʼ mar apar gangʼwen mar dwe mokwongo, joma notwe notimo nyasi mar Pasaka.
\v 20 Jodolo gi jo-Lawi nosepwodhore giwegi kendo giduto negiikore mapoth ne nyasi. Jo-Lawi noyangʼo nyarombo mar Pasaka ne joma noa e twech duto, ne owetegi ma jodolo kod gin giwegi.
\v 21 Omiyo jo-Israel mane oa e twech nochamo Pasakano, kanyakla gi jogo duto mano ngʼanyone timbe mochido mag ogendini mamoko modak machiegni kodgi mondo omi gidwar Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach Israel.
\v 22 Kuom ndalo abiriyo, negitimo Nyasi mar Makati ma ok oketie thowi gi ilo, nikech Jehova Nyasaye nosepongʼogi gi ilo kuom loko pach ruodh Asuria, mondo omi nokonygi e tich manie od Nyasaye, ma Nyasach Israel.
\c 7
\s1 Ezra obiro Jerusalem
\p 
\v 1 Bangʼ gigi duto, e kinde mar loch Artaksases ruodh Pasia, Ezra wuod Seraya, ma wuod Azaria, ma wuod Hilkia,
\v 2 ma wuod Shalum, ma wuod Zadok, ma wuod Ahitub,
\v 3 ma wuod Amaria, ma wuod Azaria, ma wuod Merayoth,
\v 4 ma wuod Zerahia, ma wuod Uzi, ma wuod Buki,
\v 5 ma wuod Abishua, ma wuod Finehas, ma wuod Eliazar, ma wuod Harun jadolo maduongʼ;
\v 6 Ezra-ni noduogo koa Babulon. Ne en japuonj man-gi lony mathoth kuom Chik Musa, ma Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach Israel, nochiwo. Ruoth nomiye gimoro amora mano kwayo, nimar lwet Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasache ne ni kuome.
\v 7 Jo-Israel mamoko, kaachiel gi jodolo, jo-Lawi, jower, jorit rangach kod jotij hekalu, bende nobiro Jerusalem e higa mar abiriyo mar Ruoth Artaksases.
\p 
\v 8 Ezra nochopo Jerusalem e dwe mar abich mar higa mar abiriyo mar ruoth.
\v 9 Nochako wuodhe koa Babulon e odiechiengʼ mokwongo mar dwe mokwongo, kendo nochopo Jerusalem e odiechiengʼ mokwongo mar dwe mar abich, nimar lwedo mangʼwon mar Nyasache ne ni kuome.
\v 10 Nimar Ezra nosechiwore owuon ne somo matut kendo rito Chik mar Jehova Nyasaye, kod puonjo chikene gi buchene e Israel.
\s1 Barup ruoth Artaksases ne Ezra
\p 
\v 11 Ma e baruwa machalre gi mane mane Ruoth Artaksases omiyo Ezra jadolo kendo japuonj, ngʼatno mosomo weche maluwore gi chike kod buche Jehova Nyasaye ne Israel:
\pmo 
\v 12 Artaksases, ruoth mar ruodhi,
\b
\pmo Ne Ezra jadolo kendo japuonj mar Chik Nyasach Polo:
\b
\pmo Amosi.
\b
\pm 
\v 13 Koro achiwo chik ni ja-Israel moro amora manie pinya, kaachiel gi jodolo kod jo-Lawi, madwaro dhi Jerusalem kodi, nyalo dhi.
\v 14 Oori gi ruoth kod jongʼadne rieko abiriyo mondo inon wach kaka Juda gi Jerusalem dhi kaluwore gi chik Nyasachi manie lweti.
\v 15 To bende, nyaka idhi gi fedha kod dhahabu ma ruoth gi jongʼadne rieko osechiwo kuom hero mag-gi giwegi ne Nyasach Israel, ma kar dak mare en Jerusalem,
\v 16 kaachiel gi fedha gi dhahabu duto ma unyalo yudo koa e gwengʼ mar Babulon, kanyakla gi chiwo ma ji kod jodolo golo ma en chiwo mar hera ne hekalu mar Nyasachgi e Jerusalem.
\v 17 Gi pesani nyaka ine ni ingʼiewo rwedhi, imbe kod nyithi rombe machwo, kanyakla gi chiwo mag-gi mag cham kod misango miolo piny, kendo gitimgo misango ewi kendo mar hekalu mar Nyasachi e Jerusalem.
\pm 
\v 18 In kod oweteni ma jo-Yahudi unyalo timo gima uneno ka ber gi fedha gi dhahabu modongʼ, kaluwore gi dwaro mar Nyasachi.
\v 19 Chiwne Nyasach Jerusalem gigo duto moket e lweti mar dendo Nyasaye e hekalu mar Nyasachi.
\v 20 Kendo gimoro amora midwaro mar hekalu mar Nyasachi ma inyalo bedo gi thuolo mar chiwo, inyalo chiwe koa e keno ma ka ruoth.
\pm 
\v 21 Koro an, Ruoth Artaksases, achiwo chik ni kuonde keno duto mag Yufrate ochiw gi chia gimoro amora ma Ezra jadolo, japuonj Chik mar Nyasach polo, nyalo kwayou, kaka
\v 22 fedha madirom kilo alufu adek gi mia angʼwen, gunde mag ngano ma pek romo kilo alufu apar gaboro, divai maromo lita alufu ariyo gi mia ariyo, mo maromo lita alufu ariyo gi mia ariyo, kod chumbi mathoth ma ok nyal pim.
\v 23 Gimoro amora ma Nyasach polo osechano, we otime gi chia ne hekalu mar Nyasach polo. En angʼo momiyo mirima dibed kuom pinyruoth gi yawuote?
\v 24 Bende nyaka ingʼe ni ionge gi teko mar chuno ji golo osuru, kata chiwo kata chudo ewi jadolo, jo-Lawi, jower, jorit rangach, jatij hekalu moro amora kata jotich mamoko e odni mar Nyasaye.
\pm 
\v 25 To in, Ezra, kaluwore gi rieko matut mar Nyasachi, ma in godo, yier jongʼad bura matindo kod jongʼad bura madongo mondo ongʼad bura gadiera ne jo-Yufrate duto, ma gin joma ongʼeyo chike Nyasachi. Kendo nyaka ipuonj ngʼato angʼata mokia chikego.
\v 26 Ngʼato angʼata ma ok luor chik Nyasachi kod chik ruoth nyaka kume e yor tho, dare, pe gige, kata tere e od twech.
\p 
\v 27 Pak obed ne Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach kwerewa, moseketo e chuny ruoth mondo luor obed ne od Jehova Nyasaye man Jerusalem e yo machalo kama
\v 28 kendo moserieyo lwete maber mar ngʼwono ne an e nyim ruoth kod jongʼadne rieko kod jotend ruoth maroteke mondo omiya luor. Nikech lwet Jehova Nyasaye Nyasacha neni kuoma, ne abedo gi chir mi achoko jotelo duto moa Israel mondo odhi koda.
\c 8
\s1 Nying kod kwan jotend dhoudi mane odwogo gi Ezra
\li4 
\v 1 Magi e jotend dhoudi kod jogo mane obiro koda koa Babulon e kinde loch Ruoth Artaksases:
\b
\li1 
\v 2 nyikwa Finehas,
\li2 Gershom;
\li1 nyikwa Ithamar,
\li2 Daniel;
\li1 nyikwa Daudi,
\li2 Hatush
\v 3 nyikwa Shekania;
\li1 nyikwa Parosh,
\li2 Zekaria, kaachiel kode ji mia achiel gi piero abich;
\li1 
\v 4 nyikwa Pahath-Moab,
\li2 Elihoyanai wuod Zerahia, kaachiel kode ji mia ariyo;
\li1 
\v 5 nyikwa Zatu,
\li2 Shekania wuod Jahaziel, kaachiel kode ji mia adek;
\li1 
\v 6 nyikwa Adin,
\li2 Ebed wuod Jonathan, kaachiel kode ji piero abich;
\li1 
\v 7 nyikwa Elam,
\li2 Jeshaya wuod Athalia, kaachiel kode ji piero abiriyo;
\li1 
\v 8 nyikwa Shefatia,
\li2 Zebadia wuod Mikael, kaachiel kode ji piero aboro;
\li1 
\v 9 nyikwa Joab,
\li2 Obadia wuod Jehiel, kaachiel kode ji mia ariyo gi apar gaboro;
\li1 
\v 10 nyikwa Bani,
\li2 Shelomith wuod Josifia, kaachiel kode ji mia achiel gi piero auchiel;
\li1 
\v 11 nyikwa Bebai,
\li2 Zekaria wuod Bebai, kaachiel kode ji piero ariyo gaboro;
\li1 
\v 12 nyikwa Azgad,
\li2 Johanan wuod Hakatan, kaachiel kode ji mia achiel gapar;
\li1 
\v 13 nyikwa Adonikam,
\li2 mago mogik, nyingegi ne Elifelet, Jeuel kod Shemaya, kaachiel kodgi ji piero auchiel;
\li1 
\v 14 nyikwa Bigvai,
\li2 Uthai kod Zakur, kaachiel kodgi ji piero abiriyo.
\s1 Duogo Jerusalem
\p 
\v 15 Ne achokogi e bath aora mamol kochiko Ahava, kendo ne wabuoro kanyo kuom ndalo adek. Kane arango e dier ji kod jodolo, ne ok ayudo jo-Lawi kanyo.
\v 16 Omiyo ne aluongo Eliezer, Ariel, Shemaya, Elnathan, Jarib, Elnathan, Nathan, Zekaria kod Meshulam, mane gin jotelo, kod Joyiarib gi Elnathan, mane gin joma osomo,
\v 17 kendo ne aorogi ir Ido, jatelo Kasifia. Ne anyisogi gima giwachne Ido kod joge, jotij hekalu man Kasifia, mondo omi gikelnwa ji ne od Nyasachwa.
\v 18 Nikech lwet Nyasachwa mar ngʼwono ne ni kuomwa, ne gikelonwa Sherebia, ngʼatno man-gi nyalo, koa e nyikwa Mali wuod Lawi, wuod Israel, kod yawuot Sherebia gi owetene, ji apar gaboro;
\v 19 kod Hashabia, kanyakla gi Jeshaya ma nyikwa Merari, kod owetene gi yawuot owetene, ji piero ariyo.
\v 20 Bende negikelo jotije hekalu mia ariyo gi piero ariyo, ma en riwruok mane Daudi kod jotelo nochako mondo okony jo-Lawi. Giduto nondik nying-gi piny.
\p 
\v 21 Bangʼ mano, ne agolo chik mondo watwe chiemo e dho aora Ahava ka wahore wawegi e nyim Nyasachwa kendo wakwaye wuoth maber ni wan gi nyithindwa, gi giwa duto.
\v 22 Wiya nokuot mar kwayo ruodh jolweny kod joriemb farese mondo ogengʼwa kuom wasikwa manie yo, nikech ne wasenyiso ruoth niya, “Lwet Nyasachwa mar ngʼwono nitie kuom ji duto moketo genogi kuome, to mirimbe mager ni kuom jogo mojwangʼe.”
\v 23 Omiyo ne watweyo chiemo kendo wakwayo Nyasachwa kuom ma, kendo nodwoko lamowa.
\p 
\v 24 Eka ne awalo jodolo motelo apar gariyo, kanyakla gi Sherebia, Hashabia kod owetegi apar,
\v 25 kendo ne apimonegi pek chiwo mar fedha gi dhahabu kod gik mane ruoth, jongʼadne rieko, jotende kod jo-Israel duto mane ni kanyo nosechiwo ne od Nyasachwa.
\v 26 Ne apimonegi pek mar fedha mane en talanta mia auchiel gi piero abich, gige fedha pekgi ne en talanta mia achiel, pek dhahabu ne en talanta mia achiel,
\v 27 bakunde piero ariyo mar dhahabu ma nengogi romo darik alufu achiel, kod gik moko ariyo mag nyinyo mowir mongʼith, bende maber ka dhahabu.
\p 
\v 28 Ne awachonegi niya, “In kaachiel gi gigi owalu tenge ne Jehova Nyasaye. Fedha gi dhahabu gin chiwo mar hera ne Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach kwereu.
\v 29 Ritgiuru ka utangʼ nyaka chop upimgi e agola mar od Jehova Nyasaye man Jerusalem e nyim jodolo motelo gi jo-Lawi kod jotend anywola mag Israel.”
\v 30 Bangʼe jodolo kod jo-Lawi noyudo fedha gi dhahabu kod gik mowal mane osepim pekgi mondo ter e od Nyasachwa e Jerusalem.
\p 
\v 31 E odiechiengʼ mar apar gariyo e dwe mokwongo ne wawuok ka waa e aora mar Ahava mondo wadhi Jerusalem. Lwet Nyasachwa ne ni kuomwa, nogengʼonwa wasigu gi jonjore mane ni e wangʼ yo.
\v 32 Omiyo ne wachopo Jerusalem, kama ne wayweyoe kuom ndalo adek.
\p 
\v 33 E odiechiengʼ mar angʼwen, e od Nyasachwa, ne wapimo pek fedha gi dhahabu kod gigo mowal ma waketo e lwet Meremoth wuod Uria, ma jadolo, Eliazar wuod Finehas ne ni kode, kod jo-Lawi bende kaka Jozabad wuod Jeshua gi Noadia wuod Binui.
\v 34 Gik moko nokwan mongʼe kar kwan-gi kod pek mag-gi, kendo pek mag-gi nondik piny e sechego.
\p 
\v 35 Eka joma ne otwe mane odwogo koa e twech nochiwo misango mar misengini miwangʼo pep ni Nyasach Israel mane gin, rwedhi apar gariyo ne jo-Israel duto, imbe piero ochiko gauchiel, nyithi rombe machwo piero abiriyo gabiriyo, to gi nywogi apar gariyo kaka misango mar golo richo. Magi duto ne gin misango miwangʼo pep ni Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 36 Bende ne gitero chike mane ruoth ochiwo ni jotend gwenge kod jotend Yufrate, bangʼe negichiwo kony ni ji kod ni od Nyasaye.
\c 9
\s1 Lemo mar Ezra kuom nyuomo nyi dhoudi mamoko
\p 
\v 1 Bangʼ ka magi duto nosetim, jotelo nobiro ira kendo owacho niya, “Jo-Israel kaachiel gi jodolo kod jo-Lawi, ok osethegore gi joma ne gikiewogo kuom yoregi mamono, kaka mago mag jo-Kanaan, jo-Hiti, jo-Perizi, jo-Jebus, jo-Amon, jo-Moab, jo-Misri kod jo-Amor.
\v 2 Gisekawo nyi joma ok jo-Yahudi, makoro odak e pinygi, kendo yawuotgi bende gisekendonegi nyi jogo. Kamano, oganda maler mar Nyasaye osedwanyore gi joma ok jo-Yahudi. To jotelo gi jodongo ema osebedo joketho moloyoe jomoko.”
\p 
\v 3 Kane awinjo wachno, ne ayiecho kandhona kod lepa, apudho yie wiya kod yie tika mi abedo piny ka an-gi bwok malich.
\v 4 Eka jogo duto mane oluoro wach Nyasach Israel nochokore buta nikech gima rach mane joma odwogo koa e twech Babulon otimo. Kendo ne abedo kanyo ka an-gi bwok malich nyaka ochopo sa misango mar odhiambo.
\p 
\v 5 Kane ochopo sa misango mar odhiambo, ne achungo aa kama ne abetie, gi kandhona kod lepa koyiech, mi apodho gi chonga ka atingʼo bedena malo ne Jehova Nyasaye Nyasacha.
\v 6 Kendo ne alemo kama:
\pm “Nyasacha, an-gi wichkuot malich kod kuyo ma ok anyal tingʼo wangʼa malo kangʼiyi, nikech richowa boyo moyombo wiyewa kendo kethowa osechopo e polo.
\v 7 Koa e ndalo mar kwerewa nyaka chil kawuono, wasebedo joketho ahinya. Nikech richo ma wasetimo, ruodhi mag pinje mamoko osenegowa kaachiel gi ruodhiwa kod jodolo mag-wa kendo giseterowa e twech kendo yako gigewa, mi wasebedo gi wichkuot maduongʼ nyaka chil kawuono.
\pm 
\v 8 “To koro sani, kuom kinde matin, Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa osebedo jangʼwono moweyonwa joma otony kendo omiyowa kama wanyalo dakie e kari maler mar lemo. Isedwogo chunywa, kendo iweyonwa thuolo mondo dendwa oduogi e twech ma wantiereni.
\v 9 Kata bed ni wan wasumbini kamano, to Nyasachwa pod ok ojwangʼowa e twech marwa. Osemiyowa ngʼwonone e nyim wangʼ ruodhi mag Pasia: Osemiyowa ngima manyien mondo oger manyien od Nyasachwa, to bende wager kuonde momukore, kendo osebedonwa kaka ohinga molworo Juda kod Jerusalem.
\pm 
\v 10 “To sani, yaye Nyasachwa, en angʼo ma wanyalo wacho bangʼ ma? Nimar ok waseluoro chike
\v 11 mane imiyowa kokalo kuom jotichni ma jonabi, kiwacho ni, ‘Piny ma udonje mondo ukaw en piny mopongʼ gi anjawo mag joge. Kuom timbegi mamono gisepongʼo pinyni gi chido margi koa giko koni nyaka giko kocha.
\v 12 Emomiyo, kik uchiw nyiu mondo kend gi yawuotgi, kata kawo nyigi ne yawuotu. Kik ubed gi singruok mar osiep kodgi sa moro amora, mondo omi ubed motegno kendo ucham gik mabeyo mag pinyni kendo uweye ne nyithindu kaka girkeni manyaka chiengʼ.’
\pm 
\v 13 “Gima osetimorenwa en nikech timbewa mamono kod kethowa ma ok odhi kare, to kata kamano, Nyasachwa, ne ok ikumowa moromore gi richowago, to niweyo jowa otony, mi wabedo thuolo kaka koroni.
\v 14 Bende dwachak waketh chikegi kendo wanywomre gi joma timo timbe mamono kama? Donge iyi diwangʼ kodwa matek madimi itiekwa, maonge ngʼama ditony kata achiel?
\v 15 Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach Israel, in ja-ratiro! Owewa odiechiengni kaka joma otony. Eri wan e nyimi kaka joricho ma bura oloyo, kendo nikech richowago, onge ngʼato kuomwa manyalo chungo e nyimi.”
\c 10
\s1 Ji ofulo richo mag-gi
\p 
\v 1 Kane Ezra lemo kendo hulo richo, koywak kendo kongʼielore piny e nyim od Nyasaye, oganda maduongʼ mar jo-Israel; chwo, mon kod nyithindo nochokore kolwore. Gin bende ne giywak malit.
\v 2 Eka Shekania wuod Jehiel, achiel kuom nyikwa Elam, nowachone Ezra niya, “Ok wasebedo jo-ratiro ni Nyasachwa kuom kendo nyiri ma ok jo-Yahudi. To kata ka wasetimo kamano, to jo-Israel pod nigi geno.
\v 3 Koro we walos singo e nyim Nyasachwa mondo oriemb mon-gi kod nyithindgi duto, kaluwore gi ngʼado rieko mar Ruoth Nyasachwa kod jogo moluoro chike mag Nyasachwa. We time kaluwore gi Chik.
\v 4 Chungʼ malo; wachni ni e lweti. Wabiro konyi; omiyo jiwri kendo itime.”
\p 
\v 5 Omiyo Ezra noa malo mi oketo jonabi gi jo-Lawi ma jotelo kod jo-Israel duto e bwo kwongʼruok mondo otim gima ne osepar. Omiyo negitimo kwongʼruokno.
\v 6 Eka Ezra noa e nyim od Nyasaye mi odhi e agoch Jehohanan wuod Eliashib. E sa mane en kanyo, ne ok ochamo chiemo kendo ne ok omodho pi, nikech nodhi nyime kokuyo kuom bedo maonge ratiro mar joma noa e twech.
\p 
\v 7 Eka nogo milome e Juda kod Jerusalem ni jogo duto mane oa e twech mondo ochokre Jerusalem.
\v 8 Ngʼato angʼata ma ok onenore e thuolo mar ndalo adek biro lalo gige duto, kaluwore gi gima jotelo kod jodongo ongʼado, kendo enodire oko mar chokruok mar joma noa e twech.
\b
\p 
\v 9 Kuom thuolo mar ndalo adek joma chwo moa Juda kod Benjamin duto nochokore Jerusalem. To e odiechiengʼ mar piero ariyo mar dwe mar ochiko, ji nobet e laru manie nyim od Nyasaye, ka gionge gi kwe nikech wachno kendo nikech koth ne goyogi.
\v 10 Eka Ezra ma jadolo noa malo kendo owachonegi niya, “Usebedo joma ok nikare; usekendo mond dhoudi mamoko, mumedo ketho mar jo-Israel.
\v 11 Koro miuru Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach kwereu duongʼ, kendo utim dwarone. Thegreuru gi joma ni butu kod mondeu mag dhoudi mamoko.”
\p 
\v 12 Chokruok mar ogandani duto nodwoko gi dwol maduongʼ niya, “In kare! Nyaka watim kaka iwacho.
\v 13 To nitiere ji mangʼeny kae kendo en kinde koth, omiyo ok wanyal chungʼ oko. Ewi mano wachni ok nyal losi gi ndalo achiel kata ariyo, nikech wasetimo richo maduongʼ e gini.
\v 14 We jotendwa otime e lo chokruokni duto. Eka we ngʼato ka ngʼato mosekendo nyi joma ok jo-Yahudi obi e sa moketi, kaachiel gi jodongo kod jongʼad bura moa dala ka dala, nyaka mirima mager mar Nyasachwa kuom wachni ogol kuomwa.”
\v 15 Ji duto noyie timo kamano, makmana Jonathan wuod Asahel gi Jazeya wuod Tikva, koriwe lwedo gi Meshulam kod Shabethai ja-Lawi, ema notamore.
\p 
\v 16 Omiyo joma noa e twech notimo kaka nochan. Ezra jadolo noyiero chwo mane jotend dhoudi, achiel koa e migawo mar dhoot ka dhoot, kendo giduto noluongogi gi nying-gi. E odiechiengʼ mokwongo mar dwe mar apar negibedo piny mondo ginon wechegi,
\v 17 kendo kochopo odiechiengʼ mokwongo mar dwe mokwongo negitieko gi chwo mane okendo mon moa e dhoudi mamoko.
\s1 Joma ne nigi ketho mar nyombo e dhoudi mamoko
\li4 
\v 18 Kuom nyikwa jodolo, magi ema nokendo nyi joma ok jo-Yahudi.
\li1 Koa e nyikwa Jeshua wuod Jozadak, kod owetene:
\li2 Maseya, Eliezer, Jarib gi Gedalia.
\v 19 Negitingʼo bedegi kaka singruok mar riembo mondegi, kendo kuom ketho mag-gi negichiwo im ngʼato ka ngʼato koa e kweth kaka misango mar pwodhruok e ketho.
\li1 
\v 20 Koa e nyikwa Imer:
\li2 Hanani gi Zebadia.
\li1 
\v 21 Koa e nyikwa Harim:
\li2 Maseya, Elija, Shemaya, Jehiel gi Uzia.
\li1 
\v 22 Koa e nyikwa Pashur:
\li2 Elioenai, Maseya, Ishmael, Nethanel, Jozabad gi Elasa.
\b
\li4 
\v 23 Kuom jo-Lawi ne gin:
\li2 Jozabad, Shimei, Kelaya (tiende ni Kelita), Pethahia, Juda gi Eliezer.
\li1 
\v 24 Koa kuom jower:
\li2 Eliashib.
\li1 Koa kuom jorit dhorangach:
\li2 Shalum, Telem gi Uri.
\b
\li4 
\v 25 To kuom jo-Israel mamoko:
\li1 Koa kuom nyikwa Parosh:
\li2 Ramia, Izia, Malkija, Mijamin, Eliazar, Malkija gi Benaya.
\li1 
\v 26 Koa kuom nyikwa Elam:
\li2 Matania, Zekaria, Jehiel, Abdi, Jeremoth gi Elija.
\li1 
\v 27 Koa kuom nyikwa Zatu:
\li2 Elioenai, Eliashib, Matania, Jeremoth, Zabad gi Aziza.
\li1 
\v 28 Koa kuom nyikwa Bebai:
\li2 Jehohanan, Hanania, Zabai gi Athlai.
\li1 
\v 29 Koa kuom nyikwa Bani:
\li2 Meshulam, Maluk, Adaya, Jashub, Shil gi Jeremoth.
\li1 
\v 30 Koa kuom nyikwa Pahath-Moab:
\li2 Adna, Kelal, Benaya, Maseya, Matania, Bezalel, Binui gi Manase.
\li1 
\v 31 Koa kuom nyikwa Harim:
\li2 Eliezer, Ishija, Malkija, Shemaya, Shimeon,
\v 32 Benjamin, Maluk gi Shemaria.
\li1 
\v 33 Koa kuom nyikwa Hashum:
\li2 Matenai, Matata, Zabad, Elifelet, Jeremai, Manase gi Shimei.
\li1 
\v 34 Koa kuom nyikwa Bani:
\li2 Madai, Amram, Uel,
\v 35 Benaya, Bedeya, Keluhi,
\v 36 Vania, Meremoth, Eliashib,
\v 37 Matania, Matenai gi Jasu.
\li1 
\v 38 Koa kuom nyikwa Binui:
\li2 Shimei,
\v 39 Shelemia, Nathan, Adaya,
\v 40 Maknadebai, Shashai, Sharai,
\v 41 Azarel, Shelemia, Shemaria,
\v 42 Shalum, Amaria gi Josef.
\li1 
\v 43 Koa kuom nyikwa Nebo:
\li2 Jeyel, Matithia, Zabad, Zebina, Jadai, Joel gi Benaya.
\b
\li4 
\v 44 Magi duto nokendo nyi joma ok jo-Yahudi, kendo moko kuomgi nonywolo nyithindo gi mon-gi.
